Title: Ritual Recovery
Description:
Dat witch doctor has stolen de trial. She mocks us, trying to eat de life of living things to free Mueh'zala. We still have influence over it, though. 

Together, we will overwhelm her evil circles. When you find a circle, call upon me, and we will push death aside.
ObjectivesText: Remove 3 ritual circles with Lukou's aid.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Rokhan in the Echo Isles.
